---
title: Indian Prawn, Potato & Cauliflower Korma Soup with Flatbreads, Almonds & Coriander
description: Make sure your spoon is at the ready because this korma soup is going to disappear in seconds. It has everything, roasted cauliflower and potato, baby leaves and aromatic mild curry flavours. Dip the tortilla wedges in for a bit of fun.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
